{"tid":2309534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"睇共產黨人社運歷史反思當下","createTime":"2020-12-02T15:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T15:02:06.000Z","uid":298288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e901bcb4e9e45bb5e19fb4a53914853b210551","tid":2309534,"uid":298288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://maoworks.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaoworks.blogspot.com%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=056eda38\" target=\"_blank\">https://maoworks.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，最近讀共產黨人反思自己社運策略既文集，諗住選其中依然有參考價值o既文章出來用番現代中文講下分享俾大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n好多人以爲《毛澤東選集》係毛自己寫，其實唔係，只是以佢名義發表等其他人以爲係正式文件迫D人認真睇。都有唔少問題其實同香港社運遇到的問題一樣。<br />\n文集簡介：<a href=\"https://maoworks.blogspot.com/2020/10/blog-post_31.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaoworks.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fblog-post_31.html&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=4de8ecd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://maoworks.blogspot.com/2020/10/blog-post_31.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一些中共早期的文章已經Po o左出來，得閒就會繼續update埋其他。<br />\n有興趣可以投稿一起寫：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/RxJ2qXBagw4tyFG96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FRxJ2qXBagw4tyFG96&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d6b7f782\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/RxJ2qXBagw4tyFG96</a><br />\n<br />\n認同請Push<br />\n不認同也可以亂插"},{"pid":"696039a79a5f40f6fdb6847850a70c0f24c4a1db","tid":2309534,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"唔該可唔可以幫我推兩推吖~<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/t